    <div class="card recentcard views-row">
          <div class="views-field views-field-title"><h3 class="field-content"><a href="/pages/henry-morgentaler-1923-2013" hreflang="en">Henry Morgentaler (1923-2013)</a></h3></div><div class="views-field views-field-body"><p class="field-content">Henry Morgentaler was a physician who performed abortions, acted as a reproductive rights activist, and advocated for legal access to abortions in Canada during the twentieth century. In 1969, he opened his first abortion clinic in Canada and participated in the legal/court case of R v. Morgentaler (1988), which led Canada to decriminalize abortion. Morgentaler helped establish legal access to abortions for women in Canada and advocated for the protection of women's reproductive choices under the law.</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-contributor"><strong class="views-label views-label-field-contributor">Contributors</strong><div class="field-content">  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--contributor paragraph--view-mode--default">
            <a href="/taxonomy/term/54655" hreflang="en">Sepehr Abdi-Moradi</a>
  Author:

